0x8b406238259a331B42bfFA1546057247C23aE8.description: An analog to culture built for the metaverse. Swarms portrays a decadent world where genetically modified bees engineered by a rogue AI are sent to terraform mars. Created on the Avalanche blockchain, 10000 bees are currently moving to mars.

0xa7abc3736bc5a4d3d4730eac5a1e487e56c867.description: Fırat keeps reigning as the most famous comics hero of Turkey since he came into our lives in 2007. The cartoonish life of this kid, who has a language and a world-view of his own, has glimpses of everybody's childhood one way or the other. Fırat has an answer to every situation he finds himself in. He suffers no traumas whatsoever. He never cries, even if he falls. He finds joy in falling in a cool manner. He can imagine block-buster features with rockets exploding and cars crashing one another with a slipper or a triple socket. His only concern is to grow up fast, when he finally does, he imagines he will be the coolest person on the planet. Fırat has 5 published books up to now, each of them a best seller. He now multiplies in NFT.
0xa7abc3736bc5a4d3d4730eac5a1e487e56c867.name: Firat

0xf675a87397a6239eaf95ad948670a5b19d076c.description: Love is in the Air is a masterpiece that epitomizes the unparalleled creative insurgency of Banksy’s oeuvre. Characterised by its recognisable subject, graphic force and visual directness, this iconic work has helped cement Banksy’s place as an a decisive political gadfly for our time. Particle acquired the piece at auction on 5/13/2021 and the work was subsequently donated to the non-profit Particle Foundation where the piece will remain in perpetuity. Love is in the Air is the first piece offered by Particle representing a peaceful revolution, changing the narrative of ownership, and enabling anyone to collect, experience, and enjoy the masterpiece.
0xf675a87397a6239eaf95ad948670a5b19d076c.name: Particle | Banksy Love is in the Air

0xc3e4de1ba138b6640867fbd986aa16763f36b4.description: Duality We live in a dual verse; on one side we exist with our desires, thoughts and dreams on the other we have reality. Sometimes they work and complement one another, sometimes they contradict. It’s up to you to decide when to live one or the other. The decisions we make defines who we are. Can you manifest your thoughts and dreams, or are you living a reality defined by others? Are you the protagonist of your dreams and desires? What is your reality? We hear and live with the inner voices of versions of ourselves who have emerged over time and stuck with us. This collection is an echo of ones journey reflecting the duality within him/herself; One’s reality vs. one’s subconscious. A journey that evolves alongside a reality but finds its path through dreams, desires and emotions. Every piece will focus on the concept of duality.
0xc3e4de1ba138b6640867fbd986aa16763f36b4.name: DUALITY

0x6c2e94836b3f4ab3d6048b70c2ad604554bd5d.description: Face Me! is a group of digital paintings, which I have recently came to the realization that they were a collection. As someone who is painting and creating visuals on daily basis, I have often found myself drawing abstract faces whenever I could not figure out what I wanted to draw, even as a hand-warming exercise time to time. Taking a moment out of life and looking back at all over 1000 digital paintings I have created, a collection emerged, thus Face Me! has presented itself to you. Face Me! consists of 60 faces form various styles and will be completed when all 60 are minted.
0x6c2e94836b3f4ab3d6048b70c2ad604554bd5d.name: Face Me!

0x6d5087B3082f73D42a32D85e38BC95dcceDe39.name: AvaxApes

0x6eea13e8ac1c4a7d28489427e6a0efb20a09f3.description: A theme in my work is creating systems to extract subconscious memories using analog & digital techniques. The past 2 years I’ve been experimenting with GLSL shaders as another way to extract my memory. A year in I decided I wanted to create a system for ingesting my memories and generating synthetic memories. Simultaneously, I wanted to create a system to “collaborate” with machines and giving them a new meaning via upcycling. The goal of Mimesis is to capture the memories of a person & combining them with the absorbed memories of an upcycled computer, generating new synthetic memories.
0x6eea13e8ac1c4a7d28489427e6a0efb20a09f3.name: Mimesis

0x4f42f2e7f5e3d7579be2e566930a5b67e369c8.description: 2,222 Avax Machina’s spawned during The Singularity, an event that occurs 200 years from the present day.
